cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper is about learning private language modeling for mobile keyboard suggestion using federated learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel model aggregation method with an attention mechanism, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Since the paper deals with privacy concerns, it may also belong to the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, since the proposed method aims to reduce communication cost during model aggregation, it may also belong to the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
